<p>Cody is a personable, smart and articulate young man. He is somewhat behind in school but  committed to improving his performance.  Cody is very athletic and he loves to play baseball and anything outdoors. He likes to read and play video games. He is also very responsible and recently had  a summer job working with kids and did great!  Cody has had some significant problems in his past but he is working  hard to overcome these. He is determined  to succeed and in the right, unconditionally supportive adoptive family he  will. He has tremendous potential to do  well and a loving and stable adoptive family is just what he needs to do  well. Cody was born in December, 1997. </p>
